* Task 5 fixture: minimal subprogram definition (called by MAIN.NSP)
* A .NSN subprogram that MAIN.NSP's CALLNAT 'MYSUB' should resolve to.

DEFINE DATA
LOCAL
  1 INPUT-VALUE (A20)
  1 OUTPUT-VALUE (A20)
END DEFINE

* Simple operation to demonstrate a real subroutine
MOVE INPUT-VALUE TO OUTPUT-VALUE
ADD 1 TO *COUNTER

END
